This application was created to allow seamless activities going on in Clearlinehmo company!
User(Staff & Customer) can register, Login, Reset Password.
Providers(Hospitals) can partner and render services to the Enrolee.
User can generate Enrolee Number and NHIS Authorisation code(Alphanumeric).
Enrolee can lodge complain if treatment is not well served.
User can search for his data from the database by entering his NHIS Authorisation code or Enrolee number.
Provider can verify Enrolee by his ID or Authorisation code.
And Many more functionalities.
